Credits Cinematography, James Callanan; editor, Tom Haneke; music, Michael Bacon; film producer, Amanda Pollack; executive producer, Margaret Drain.
Note Originally broadcast in February 2001 on the PBS television program: The American Experience.
Special features include: interviews with the producer and cinematographer, audio descriptions, audio navigation, three-part featurette, interactive map, videos interview of historians, timelines, essays, photo galleries, and teacher's guide.
Summary A six part program which examines the Lincolns' family life and marriage, Abraham Lincoln's presidency, and the Civil War era.
